title: Clean Flat  Icons
description: 4216 flat vector icons at 3 resolutions and 1716 buttons.
longDescription:
This is a mobile-friendly flat button icon asset. 

It include 5932 buttons and icons at each resolution. 

This pack has white buttons and icons with a clean and minimalist style. 

It can easily customize your favorite buttons and icons.

Document
technicalDetails:
Features:

- PNG files and layered PSD files；

- Resolutions:128x128,256x256,512x512;

- 4216 vector icons(2203 icons and 2013 line icons);

- 1716 buttons：

 30 circles,30 squares,30 rectangles,30 ovals;

 150 corner squares,150 corner rectangles;

 144 line circles,144 line squares,144 line rectangles,144 line ovals;

 720 line corner squares;
